<div class="dateline"><span class="type">PERMANENT LINK</span> | JANUARY 20, 2012</div>
                    <h1 class="title" id="a009411">The Optimal Capital Gains Tax Rate is Below Ten Percent</h1>

   <div class="hosted"><a href="http://econlog.econlib.org/authordhenderson.html">David Henderson</a></div>
</td>
